          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Combine the<strong> red wine vinegar</strong>, <strong>dried oregano</strong>, <strong>chopped</strong> <strong>garlic </strong>(not a big garlic fan? Try using less!) and 2 tbsp <span class=\"text-danger\">[4 tbsp]</span> <strong>olive oil </strong>in a small bowl<strong> </strong>with a pinch of <strong>sugar</strong>, <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong> – this is your <strong>vinaigrette</strong></p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-6-1624621414871-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
